One day I was sitting at my PC and I suddenly had an idea for an original level. Taking advantage of the physics engine, I created a level out of blocks which could be demolished. Randomly spawned blocks pummel this structure until it collapses, as people desperately run about on top of it. Death is guaranteed eventually... but who will be the last man standing?

Sadly guns had to be removed, as it mucks up the physics. If it becomes all jolty and slow you have to end the round in some way.

mp_restartgame 1

Enjoy this map! I have always been interested in physics and hopefully more levels like this will be out soon. There have been loads of versions of this level, though this is one of the most balanced. (Originated from my old GpX_Smash levels, but then my clan changed)

This was originally jD_gibvalley, as that was my clan when I made it. However, since I took over the clan I have changed the name numerous times, currently it is Dsltn. I made this map within one day and it wasn't intentionally surf. however, once I found out how fun it was its popularity grew and has been a hit with most people on the server.

sv_airaccelerate 2000 (helps with surfing)

There are loads of things to discover on this map and it's a great to muck about with stuff, such as knife fights on the planes (shoot the bars to let them swoop down), and it's great to knife noobs once you've mastered the surf.

Please give this map a chance, as it's more fun once you're used to it.

This map is a css coop fun map with hdr, the objective is to destroy as many boxes as you can, to know how many you have destroyed just
check your score.
Do not kill the other players, unless you want to ruin the game, just wait until they die killed by the boxes.

If you want to play it alone with bots, create a server and add bots and write bot_dont_shoot 1 in console.

As this they will rarely hit with their knives.

To install just unzip in your css/maps directory, everything is bspzipped inside!

Then join or create a server and have fun!

This map is better with some friends that on a server, cause people often just ruins the game by killing everyone.

***IMPORTANT***

Known Issue : If you let too many boxes to spawn, it will crash the game.

Solution : Destroy as many boxes as you can.

This is a fun map with SMGs only in a cave. the map is split up in 2 similar sections (bombsites). one is marked with red, the other with yellow. both sections are sealed by gates which open on touch. they are to prevent spawn killing and close after 10 seconds after they have been opened.

The Rollers are on the side of the bomb area that is marked with a glow, they push the players to the outside of it and if they fall off they die.

The map most likely will result in sprayfests and could be laggy in 32 vs 32 so its recomended to play on 24 vs 24. The map is made in fy style to prevent everyone taking the same weapon. for more information read the textfile with the map.

Hi,

this is my first map. It has been created with motives from cs_dustjump out of CS 1.6. I hope you like it.

Try to land in one of the three pools, one of the three cloth canopies (middle) or the well to survive the jump. Down in each of the houses is one teleporter to quickly return to the top.

This map is for max. 30 Players !


The Zip-file includes two versions:

de dustjump       - AWP and auto sniper are disabled.

de dustjump all   - All weapons can be used.


Otherwise both versions are exactly the same (v 1.2).


This map was created by: second ich
2010

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Unpack the Zip-file and move the file "de dustjump" or "de dustjump all" (or both) to:

Steam/SteamApps/"your name"/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps
